Name: Explorations complete!
Description: Perhaps you can use the information you've gleaned...

DefaultEvent.Name: The islands of the Empire
DefaultEvent.Description: All of them warrant further attention. For now though, it would be best to see if your initial discoveries can whet the interest of anyone back home.

ChildBranches.Name: Prepare a Comprehensive Port Report
ChildBranches.Description: Few have reason to brave the waters this far East, especially with the trade embargo. The Admiralty will pay especially well for up-to-date intelligence.
